{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji51.pdf"],"article":{"title":"对罗瑞卿来信的批语","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"对罗瑞卿来信\"的批语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1973年11月20日）似可释放。请中央酌定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1973，11，20"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]罗瑞卿，1973年11月15日给毛泽东写信说，我现在满身是病，两腿伤残，恳求主席和党解除对我的关押，给我一定限度的自由。毛泽东批示后不久，罗瑞卿即被解除监禁。1975年6月，罗瑞卿恢复了党的组织生活，并担任中央军委顾问。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1973,"month":11,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":444,"page_end":444},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"罗瑞卿","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"批示"}]}]}